OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will remain
OL,8,Fdry with some lengthy clear periods.
OL,9,FCold with rural frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,12,Fwith some good spells of sunshine.
OL,13,FClouding over from the north through
OL,14,Fthe evening with some light showery
OL,15,Frain. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
