OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FEarly
OL,6,Fshowery rain on Monday then dry and
OL,7,Fbright. Early showers on Tuesday then
OL,8,Fdry and bright for a time before more
OL,9,Fshowers later. Cool with widespread
OL,10,Fshowers on Wednesday.
